data.description: Current VA loan is Assumable and rate is 2.5% for buyers that qualify for VA benefits. Two story home with three bedrooms and two and a half bath. HVAC system was installed in 2021 with split zone and separate thermostats for up and down stairs. Granite counter tops in the spacious kitchen over looking the patio and Antelope Creek. Situated in a family-friendly neighborhood and within a 10 minute walk to Sunset East Park!
